.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVk3psM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVk3psM.jpg&h=4050b9a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中港食客無牛不歡　禍延雨林</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190825/20755525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190825%2F20755525&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=6e8487a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190825%2F20755525&h=66b84008\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190825/20755525</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zFiXAR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zFiXAR.png&h=62deb993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">The Amazon is burning because the world eats so much meat</span><br />\nBy Eliza Mackintosh, CNN<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2019/08/23/americas/brazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2019%2F08%2F23%2Famericas%2Fbrazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl%2Findex.html&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=e9a9630b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2019%2F08%2F23%2Famericas%2Fbrazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl%2Findex.html&h=216c3621\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2019/08/23/americas/brazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當大家打緊國際輸出革命，全球各國都幫緊香港人發聲既時候，另一單近期最大既新聞就係亞馬遜森林火燭，而香港竟然係入口最多牛肉既地方？？？<br />\n<br />\n唔該，依家香港軟實力啱啱先建立到，出國同人講自己係香港人，人地都會知你係民主鬥士，你唔會想又加返條破壞環境既罪名呀嘛？ 就算無人怪香港人，依個都係再次展現香港人人性光輝既重要機會！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知香港其實只係做轉口港，但做PR 唔好淨係成日掛住理真相係點<br />\n<br />\n政治d睇件事，如果香港人肯發起戒食牛行動到全世界都知道，今次會係一個為香港人branding既絕佳輸出革命機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">即刻發起戒食牛肉行動！！！！<br />\n以示香港人面向國際，對國際社會既責任感！！！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0effdf12eae15844140b1241f62e57f418a9097d","tid":1506163,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f22653de9c8a24e385b543b4c9426c6d75eefed","tid":1506163,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"562efc39ede07798a0920f584c157b0c532ca85d","tid":1506163,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70bd5cc24e3822d8ccaf5e76c83a06ac0beb0abd","tid":1506163,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:25:55.000Z","msg":"沙田挾度歡迎既片/youtube link"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:33:41.000Z","msg":"有冇原片可以post比我save，fb見到 但save唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sor"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:34:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/77xWR0agV2I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F77xWR0agV2I&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=0c738ae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/77xWR0agV2I</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:36:42.000Z","msg":"謝謝 聽日會send!<img src=\"/